  "title": "Site Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Title</p>\n<p>Site Engineer</p>\n<p>Occupation</p>\n<p>Site Engineer</p>\n<h5>Job Description &amp; Requirements</h5>\n<h5>Job Description &amp; Requirements</h5>\n<p>1. TO ASSIST PROJECT MANAGER IN OVERALL PLANNING, MONITORING &amp; ORGANIZING ON THE PROJECT.</p>\n<p>2. TO PLAN DAY TO DAY WORK PROGRAMME &amp; OVERSEE OF THE PROJECT PROGRESS.</p>\n<p>3. DAILY SITE ARRANGEMENT FOR MANPOWER &amp; MACHINERIES.</p>\n<p>4. TO LIAISE WITH SUBCONTRACTORS &amp; ENSURE TIMELY COMPLETION OF ALL WORKS ACCORDING TO QUALITY SPECIFICATION &amp; WORK SCHEDULE.</p>\n<p>5. TO EVALUATE &amp; RESOLVE ANY DISCREPANCIES &amp; PROBLEMS ARISING AT SITE (TECHNICAL MATTERS).</p>\n<p>6. TO MANAGE, SUPERVISE &amp; COORDINATE SITE WORKS &amp; WORKERS.</p>\n<p>7. TO SUPERVISE &amp; ENSURE QUALITY OF WORKS ACHIEVED &amp; TO COMPLY WITH SAFETY &amp; ENVIRONMENTAL REGULATIONS.</p>\n<p>8. TO ENSURE WORKERS COMPLY WITH THE COVID-19 REGULATION</p>\n<p>9. WILLINGLY TO HELP OUT IF SHORT OF MANPOWER</p>",
