    "uen": "199601459C",
    "description": "<p><strong>Beng Heng Engineering Pte Ltd</strong> was incorporated in 1996 as a private limited company under the laws of Singapore. Our Company is registered with <strong>BCA</strong>under trade <strong>CR03</strong> – <strong>Demolition, CW02 – Civil Engineering </strong>and<strong> Workplace Safety Health Council, bizSAFE Star; ISO 45001</strong>. Over the years, we have revolved on mixed construction activities including General Building, Civil Engineering Construction and Rental of Excavators and Breakers and supply recycle concrete aggregate.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our company is engaged in providing specialised and professional services in General Building, Approved Asbestos Removal Contractor, Civil Engineering, Golf Course Construction and Improvement Works.</p>\n<p>We have a team of passionate people whom are always striving to provide the most cost effective, timely and quality construction services to our customer. For us, our customers deserved the best.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our success in securing repeated orders from established Clients is testament to our commitment to quality service and total customer satisfaction. We believe a satisfied customer is our greatest gratification for a job well done.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>OUR QUALITY POLICY</strong></p>\n<p>To provide <strong>TOTAL CUSTOMER SATISFACTORY</strong> by maintaining reliable, prompt, excellent quality service at a competitive rate with <strong>SAFETY</strong> come first at all times.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>OUR QUALITY OBJECTIVE</strong></p>\n<p>To complete projects within agreed schedule and deliver results exceeding customers' expectation.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To achieve this objective, the company will unceasingly upgrade the skills of its staff and deploy the most advanced plant, equipment, technology and work procedures available in the industry.</p>",
